text: America's Next Top Model, Cycle 5 was the fifth season of America's Next Top Model. There were 13 contestants. The winner was 18-year-old Nicole Linkletter. ==Prizes== * A modeling contract with Ford Models * A spread in Elle * A $100,000 contract with CoverGirl ==Contestants== (In alphabetical order) * Ashley Black * Lisa D'Amato * Diane Hern치ndez * Cassandra Jean * Kyle Kavanagh * Nicole Linkletter * Erika "Nik" Pace * Sarah Rhoades * Jayla Rubinelli * Brittany "Bre" Scullark * Kimberly "Kim" Stolz * Ebony Taylor * Coryn Woitel ==Episodes== 1\. casting episode 2\. *Best: Nik Pace *Worst: Sarah Rhoades & Ashley Black *Eliminated: Ashley Black 3\. *Best: Cassandra Jean *Worst: Diane Hern치ndez & Ebony Taylor *Eliminated: Ebony Taylor 4\. *Quit: Cassandra Jean *Best: Jayla Rubinelli *Worst: Sarah Rhoades & Kim Stolz *Eliminated: Sarah Rhoades 5\. *Best: Kyle Kavanagh *Worst: Bre Scullark & Diane Hern치ndez *Eliminated: Diane Hern치ndez 6\. *Best: Lisa D'Amato *Worst: Nik Pace & Coryn Woitel *Eliminated: Coryn Woitel 7\. *Best: Kim Stolz *Worst: Kyle Kavanagh & Bre Scullark *Eliminated: Kyle Kavanagh 8\. *Best: Bre Scullark *Worst: Jayla Rubinelli & Nicole Linkletter *Eliminated: None 9\. *Best: Kim Stolz *Worst: Lisa D'Amato & Jayla Rubinelli *Eliminated: Lisa D'Amato 10\. *Best: Nik Pace *Worst: Bre Scullark & Kim Stolz *Eliminated: Kim Stolz 11\. *Best: Nicole Linkletter *Worst: Bre Scullark & Jayla Rubinelli *Eliminated: Jayla Rubinelli 12\. *Best: Nik Pace *Worst: Nicole Linkletter & Bre Scullark *Eliminated: Bre Scullark *Final Two: Nik Pace & Nicole Linkletter *Winner: Nicole Linkletter 05
